Sentence: Recently, endohedral fullerenes such as Sc@C , Y@C 82 , La@C 82 , Gd@C 82 , La 2 @C 80 , and Sc 2 @C 84 have been syn- thesized in large quantities.
For example, the monomeric structure of Cs 6 C 60 is stable up to 45 GPa while Rb 6 C 60 shows a structural transition to a two-dimensional (2D) poly- meric structure above 35 GPa and 600 K.
